response.overview: Ice water runs through the veins of your top 5 picks. Evil heels all of them, and a dozens stars of the business count down your selections and tell you what they think along the way.  This is where you got to choose who was the best at making us hate them. Who was MOST effective in generating that heat? Well you voted, and here’s your countdown.  A dozen stars in all original interviews!  It’s WRESTLING’S MOST…EFFECTIVE HEEL!
response.title: Wrestling’s Most…Effective Heel
